metadata.name: EVE Genesis
metadata.description:
The official pre-reveal image of "EVE". Minted as an Open Edition. 

EVE, a generative human art drop. A mesmerizing collection unlike any other. Each version, with its multitude of carefully crafted traits and variations, ensures a one-of-a-kind piece of art. Get ready to be captivated by her intricate beauty. Reject the homogenization of art by AI prompts. Embrace the beauty of human creation. 

The Collecteve is formed with "EVE", the Collecteon will be finalized with "EON".
